00:02:30.750 --> 00:02:35.470
Wu Yang!

00:02:40.630 --> 00:02:42.680
Wu Yang!

00:02:48.630 --> 00:02:50.630
Who was so cruel

00:02:50.870 --> 00:02:53.800
