00:03:08.150 --> 00:03:09.680
-Wu Yang!
-Auntie Chi Ying!

00:03:10.190 --> 00:03:13.400
Wu Yang!

00:03:20.520 --> 00:03:20.960
Huan.

00:03:20.960 --> 00:03:21.560
Wu Yang...

00:03:21.590 --> 00:03:22.990
