00:10:50.120 --> 00:10:50.630
Master,

00:10:51.150 --> 00:10:53.030
where are we heading to look for clues?

00:10:53.030 --> 00:10:53.440
Do you think

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:54.900
I'm here to look for clues?

00:10:56.360 --> 00:10:57.420
Then what are we...

